The little Taco shop

The Little Taco Shop" is a beginner-friendly web development project designed to practice and demonstrate core HTML and CSS skills.The project simulates a basic restaurant website for a fictional taco shop. This helpsiin understanding of website structure, semantic tags, and styling fundamentals.
